examples.en: Let's eat, drink, and be merry!

счастливого рождества!, поздравляю с праздником рождества!

examples.en: When other people were merry, Mrs. Varden was dull.

examples.en: We wish you a Merry Christmas.

examples.en: He could hear them uttering merry speeches.

examples.en: They sang a merry little song.
Christmas is a time to eat, drink and make merry.

examples.en: We wish you a Merry Christmas and a Happy New Year!

examples.en: He's a lovely man with merry eyes and a wide smile.

examples.en: Shakespeare called it “the merry month of May.”

examples.en: He marched off, whistling a merry tune.

examples.en: I wish you all a merry Christmas.

examples.ru: Всех с Рождеством и с Новым Годом!
